description:
Chromatica Ordinals is an art collection by Resaang, a collection that transcends digital and physical boundaries and showcases the intersections of technology, art and human creativity on a canvas and an NFT.

The project exists at the crossroads of art and blockchain but also challenges the way we perceive and value art. A very physical medium of acrylic paint immortalized in Block 78 SATs.
name: Chromatica Ordinals
